 docs/appendices/release-notes/6.0.3.rst       |  3 +
 .../execution/dml/IndexDocumentBuilder.java   |  8 +--
 .../io/crate/execution/dml/ObjectIndexer.java |  8 ++-
 .../io/crate/execution/dml/IndexerTest.java   | 62 +++++++++++--------
 5 files changed, 48 insertions(+), 36 deletions(-)

diff --git a/docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.13.rst b/docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.13.rst
index a9ba1c52d9..372ce16c36 100644
--- a/docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.13.rst
+++ b/docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.13.rst
@@ -59,3 +59,6 @@ Fixes
 - Fixed an issue that caused ``ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsExeption`` when executing
   ``COPY FROM`` on a table containing non-deterministic generated or default
   columns.
+
+- Fixed an issue where null-valued sub-columns of objects were omitted when
+  queried.
